\mt1 Titus
\is1 Introduction
\ip Si Titu, kene sikandin Hudiyu and kene egpalintutuu dengan te God. Piru hengkayi te mewuri e timpu na-Kristuwanen e sikandin. Ne puun dutu, neyimu sikandin talagbulig of Paul te me himu rin. The seini sulat, impeuyan of Paul diye te kandin te inggaat din diye te Krita eyew eg-uyan te punduk te migmalintutuu. (The Krita, pulu te dahat sakup te Grisya.)
\ip Ne due tatelu impanengneng te seini sulat: The first, impasuman-suman si Titu ke nekey ka eleg egbatasanen te me pangulu te migmalintutuu. Keilangan egpakataha sikandin kayi tenged su masulug ka mareet batasan te matig-Krita and due masulug talagpanulu kene malehet egpasuwey te migmalintutuu.
\ip The igkarangeb, intambahan si Titu ke egmenuwen din te pegpanulu ka nalein-lein people diye te punduk te migmalintutuu, lagkes seeye se me lukes-lukes and me uripen, and seeye se bayew e me buyag me lukes and women. (Ne iyan egpanulu te me mengebay ka buyag e women.)
\ip Te katammanan, migtambahan of Paul si Titu concerning the Kristuwanen peg-ugpe, and pegpanalliya te peg-ehet te duma, pegpaapuley, and pegbaad-baad diye te punduk te migmalintutuu. Impasuman-suman man‑e of Paul si Titu egpakatuman ki te seeye se insuhu kanta tenged te kaluwasan imbehey kanta of Hisu Kristu.
\ip Egkeupian si Paul egkanengnengan kayi te seini sulat amana impurtanti diye te migmalintutuu ka peggimu te meupiya (1:6; 2:7,14; 3:1,8-9,14) piru kene sika egpakaluwas (3:5).
